    </div>
    <p><strong>Ideal para:</strong> quem quer entrar no universo HJC com segurança e gastar pouco.</p>
    <div class="btn-buy-container">
      <a href="https://amzn.to/4iX2pbH" class="btn-buy" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">Ver na Amazon</a>
      <a href="https://mercadolivre.com/sec/1JeVyNQ" class="btn-buy ml" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">Ver no Mercado Livre</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="product-section">
    <h3>5. Capacete Moto HJC RPHA 90s Com Óculos Solar</h3>
    <div class="h2-image-card product-image">
